📰 BLOGS
1️⃣ GET /api/blogs

📌 Purpose: সব ব্লগ লিস্ট করা, pagination সহ

✅ Request Example:

GET /api/blogs?page=1&category=tech&tag=react&search=animation


✅ Response:

{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "10 React Tricks You Should Know",
      "slug": "10-react-tricks-you-should-know",
      "excerpt": "Learn how to optimize your React app...",
      "thumbnail": "https://picsum.photos/800/400",
      "views": 452,
      "upvotes": 22,
      "downvotes": 3,
      "category": {
        "id": 3,
        "name": "Technology",
        "slug": "technology"
      },
      "tags": [
        { "id": 1, "name": "React" },
        { "id": 4, "name": "Frontend" }
      ],
      "published_at": "2025-09-25T12:30:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "meta": {
    "current_page": 1,
    "last_page": 5,
    "total": 50
  }
}

2️⃣ GET /api/blogs/{slug}

📌 Purpose: একক ব্লগ ডিটেইলস, views count + comments সহ

✅ Request:

GET /api/blogs/10-react-tricks-you-should-know


✅ Response:

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "10 React Tricks You Should Know",
  "slug": "10-react-tricks-you-should-know",
  "content": "<p>React Hooks are powerful...</p>",
  "views": 453,
  "upvotes": 22,
  "downvotes": 3,
  "category": { "id": 3, "name": "Technology" },
  "tags": [
    { "id": 1, "name": "React" },
    { "id": 4, "name": "Frontend" }
  ],
  "comments": [
    {
      "id": 11,
      "user_name": "Sifat",
      "comment_text": "Very helpful!",
      "created_at": "2025-10-01T10:00:00Z",
      "replies": [
        {
          "id": 12,
          "user_name": "Admin",
          "comment_text": "Thanks, glad you liked it!",
          "is_admin_reply": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

3️⃣ POST /api/blogs

📌 Purpose: নতুন ব্লগ তৈরি করা (Admin only)

✅ Request (JSON):

{
  "title": "Mastering Framer Motion",
  "excerpt": "Animate your React apps with Framer Motion.",
  "content": "<p>Framer Motion is an animation library...</p>",
  "thumbnail": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "category_id": 2,
  "tag_ids": [1, 3, 5],
  "published_at": "2025-10-09 10:00:00"
}


✅ Response:

{
  "message": "Blog created successfully.",
  "data": {
    "id": 25,
    "title": "Mastering Framer Motion",
    "slug": "mastering-framer-motion",
    "tags": [
      { "id": 1, "name": "Animation" },
      { "id": 3, "name": "React" }
    ]
  }
}

4️⃣ PUT /api/blogs/{id}

📌 Purpose: ব্লগ আপডেট করা

✅ Request:

{
  "title": "Mastering Framer Motion in 2025",
  "excerpt": "Updated guide with new tricks.",
  "tag_ids": [2, 4]
}


✅ Response:

{
  "message": "Blog updated successfully."
}

5️⃣ DELETE /api/blogs/{id}

📌 Purpose: ব্লগ ডিলিট করা (Admin only)

✅ Response:

{
  "message": "Blog deleted successfully."
}

💬 COMMENTS
6️⃣ POST /api/blogs/{id}/comment

📌 Purpose: নতুন কমেন্ট করা বা রিপ্লাই

✅ Request:

{
  "user_name": "Sifat",
  "comment_text": "Nice write-up!",
  "parent_id": null
}


✅ Response:

{
  "message": "Comment added successfully.",
  "data": {
    "id": 44,
    "user_name": "Sifat",
    "comment_text": "Nice write-up!",
    "created_at": "2025-10-09T10:12:00Z"
  }
}

7️⃣ POST /api/blogs/{id}/comment/reply

📌 Purpose: রিপ্লাই টু কমেন্ট / admin reply

✅ Request:

{
  "user_name": "Admin",
  "comment_text": "Appreciate your feedback!",
  "parent_id": 44,
  "is_admin_reply": true
}


✅ Response:

{
  "message": "Reply added successfully."
}

👍 VOTES
8️⃣ POST /api/blogs/{id}/vote

📌 Purpose: IP-based upvote / downvote

✅ Request:

{
  "vote_type": "up"
}


✅ Response (First time):

{
  "message": "Vote recorded.",
  "upvotes": 23,
  "downvotes": 3
}


✅ Response (Same IP again):

{
  "message": "You have already voted.",
  "upvotes": 23,
  "downvotes": 3
}

🏷️ TAGS
9️⃣ GET /api/tags

📌 Purpose: সব ট্যাগ দেখা

✅ Response:

[
  { "id": 1, "name": "React", "slug": "react" },
  { "id": 2, "name": "Laravel", "slug": "laravel" },
  { "id": 3, "name": "Tailwind", "slug": "tailwind" }
]

🗂️ CATEGORIES
🔟 GET /api/categories

📌 Purpose: সব ক্যাটেগরি দেখা

✅ Response:

[
  { "id": 1, "name": "Technology", "slug": "technology" },
  { "id": 2, "name": "Design", "slug": "design" }
]
